-- 
2011-05-05T05:35:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/turkish-opposition-objects-to-trainee-imams-in-police-star-says.html
Turkey ’s main opposition party applied
to the Constitutional Court to cancel recent legislation
allowing the graduates of schools training Imams to enter the
